<i>adjective</i>: 버겁다 [버겁따], 겹다 [겹ː따] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>버겁다 [버겁따]</dt><br>
<dd>unmanageable; be too much for</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 하거나 살아가는 데 능력이 미치지 못해 힘들다.</dd><br>
<dd>Having difficulty in doing something or making a living due to lack of ability.</dd><br>
<dt>겹다 [겹ː따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. too much for; unmanageable</dd><br>
<dd>정도가 지나쳐서 참거나 견뎌 내기가 어렵다.</dd><br>
<dd>The degree of something being overly high, so that one is unable to bear it.</dd><br>
<dd>2. too emotional</dd><br>
<dd>거세게 일어나는 어떤 감정이나 정서에 깊이 빠지다.</dd><br>
<dd>Falling deeply into a wild emotion or mood.</dd><br>
<dd>3. too late</dd><br>
<dd>철이나 때가 한참 지나서 늦다.</dd><br>
<dd>Too late or far behind in time or season.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>